sndwrks documentation — Licensing
==================================

This repository contains two kinds of material, licensed differently:

* Documentation content — the prose, images, diagrams, screenshots, and
  other written material (primarily under `src/content/`, `src/assets/`,
  and `public/`) — is proprietary. All rights reserved (see below).

* Software — the source code, configuration, build scripts, and tooling
  (for example `astro.config.mjs`, files under `src/pages/`, `src/styles/`,
  `scripts/`, and the GitHub workflows) — is licensed under the MIT License
  (see below).

Where a file could be considered both, the more specific intent governs:
written documentation is proprietary; code is MIT.


